[[div class="nametag"]]
+ Bedrock
[[module Rate]]
[[/div]]

**Bedrock** is an aesthetic base theme created by [[*user EstrellaYoshte]], [[*user Liryn]] and [[*user Placeholder McD]], with special thanks to [[*user aismallard]] for assistance with GitHub, and [[*user Woedenaz]] for the Edit Area button SVGs alongside general consulting.

This serves as the foundational structure for [[[theme:basalt|Basalt 2.0]]].

